## Limitations

- The report relies on available online sources, which may not cover all scientific studies or expert opinions on vaccine safety.
- Some sources may have inherent biases, either pro-vaccine or anti-vaccine, which could influence the presentation of information.
- The rapidly evolving nature of vaccine research, especially concerning COVID-19, means that new data could emerge that may alter current understandings of vaccine safety.

